## About

> 
>
> UI Ticket generator is inspired by ticket from Next.js Conf 2020    
>
> 

<img width="100%" alt="UI ticket generator" src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/JonatasT/Ui-ticket-generator/main/public/uitgengif.gif"/>



### First install dependencies

First, install the dependencies
```bash
yarn install
```

### Run server

Finally, run the development server:

```bash
yarn run dev
# or
yarn dev
```

### It's done!

Open [http://localhost:3000](http://localhost:3000) with your browser to see the result.
